{"title":"Resin Transfer Moulding (RTM)","markdown":{"headingText":"Resin Transfer Moulding (RTM)","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"{{< include macros.qmd >}}\n\n### RTM: context\n\n::: {.columns}\n\n::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n\nManufacturing composite materials\n\n**Uses of composite materials:** Aerospace, automotive and marine industries. \n\n**Benefits:** High-performance, lightweight, flexibility to accommodate complex designs\n\n**Manufacturing Involves:**  \\textit{Automatic Fibre Placement:} A robotic system lays down fibre tapes into a tool. \\textit{Resin Transfer Molding (RTM).} \n\n\n:::\n\n::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n\n![](Figs/B787_composite.jpg){width=100%}\n\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n\n## RTM: Process{.scrollable}\n\n\n![](Figs/RTM1.jpg){width=100%}\n\n\n\n\n## Defects in RTM\n\n::: {layout-ncol=2}\n![](Figs/ICIAM2.jpg)\n\n![](Figs/ICIAM3.jpg)\n:::\n\n## Inverse Problem in RTM\n\n[**Objective:**]{.alert} Infer physical properties of the reinforcement given pressure measurements during resin injection.\n\n\n[**Application:**]{.alert} Active control and Non-destructive Evaluation (NDE)\n\n::: {.columns}\n\n::: {.column width=\"70%\"}\n\n```{=html}\n<div style=\"\n  width:100%;\n  display:flex;\n  justify-content:center;\n  align-items:flex-start;\n\">\n  <video id=\"rtmvid\"\n         controls\n         autoplay\n         muted\n         loop\n         playsinline\n         style=\"\n           max-height:60vh;\n           max-width:100%;\n           border-radius:12px;\n         \"\n         onloadedmetadata=\"this.currentTime = 20;\">\n    <source src=\"videos/RTM.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n  </video>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n\n::: {.column width=\"30%\"}\n\n\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n\n## Resin Injection Model\n\n\n::: {.columns}\n\n::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n\n::: callout-note\n\n## Forward Problem: \n\nFind $(\\blue{p,\\Upsilon})$ given  $\\red{u}=\\red{(\\kappa,\\phi)}$.\n\nDarcy flow:\n$$\n- \\nabla \\cdot \\Big[ \\frac{ \\red{\\kappa(x)}}{\\mu} \\nabla \\blue{p(x,t)} \\Big] = 0,\\quad \\textrm{in}~ \\Omega(t) \\nonumber\n$$\nMoving front: $x\\in \\Upsilon(t)$:\n$$ \\frac{d \\blue{\\Upsilon(t)}}{dt}=  -  \\frac{\\red{\\kappa(x)}}{\\red{\\phi(x)} \\mu} \\nabla \\blue{p(x,t)} \\cdot \\mathbf{n}(x,t) \\nonumber\n$$\n:::\n\n:::\n\n::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n\n![](Figures/resin_domain2.png)\n\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n::: callout-important\n\n## Inverse Problem\n\nFind $\\red{(\\kappa(x),\\phi(x))}$ given measurements of $\\blue{p(x_{1}),\\dots,p(x_{M})}$.\n\n:::\n\n## Goal 1: Characterisation of material properties (with uncertainty)\n\n![](Figs/Goal1.png)\n\n## Goal 2: Calibrated Model (for active control)\nNeeds deep learning surrogate!\n\n![](Figures/Experiment4.png)\n\n\n\n[[Back to Applications menu]{.button}](index.html#apps-hub)\n\n\n## Prior\n\n![](Figures/prior_pairs.png)\n\n## Posterior\n\n\n![](Figures/posterior_pairs.png)\n\n<div class=\"backhub\">\n  ↩ <a href=\"index.html\">Volver al inicio</a>\n</div>\n[[Back to Applications menu]{.button}](#apps-hub)\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"clean-revealjs":{"identifier":{"display-name":"RevealJS","target-format":"clean-revealjs","base-format":"revealjs","extension-name":"clean"},"execute":{"fig-width":10,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":false,"output":true,"warning":false,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":false,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":true,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":f